**Overview**  

This dashboard provides a comprehensive view of events captured by Cisco Secure Endpoint. It includes a line chart showing trends in events over time, a total events count metric, pie charts that break down events by severity and file disposition, bar charts that display threat tactics and techniques, and a saved search that provides essential details about the events for deeper investigation.

[Integration Page](/app/integrations/detail/cisco_secure_endpoint/overview)
